title: Ebey's Landing National Historical Reserve: Photos & Multimedia
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia             Photos & Multimedia        Farms like this one and the surrounding natural beauty are part of what makes Ebey's Reserve so special. NPS Photo (H. Richards)         Desktop Backgrounds  Download a new desktop background calendar each month to help you enjoy the reserve wherever you are working. A new image from the reserve will be used every month.  Step 1: Click on one of the different screen sizes below to download the image to your computer. Step 2: Set the image as your desktop background.  Tip - If the image does look quite right, try using one of the other image sizes.   JANUARY: Jacob and Sarah Ebey House in Winter  1024 x 786 (1.7 MB) 1280 x 1024 (2.5 MB)  1920 x 1080 (3.7 MB)   February: The Ferry House and the Straight of Juan De Fuca   Medium size monitor - 1024 x 786 (1.5 MB) Large size monitor- 1280 x 1024 (2.4 MB) Very large size monitor - 2560 x 1600   Photo Galleries                  Scenes from the Reserve   50 Photos  In all seasons, the town of Coupeville and the prairies of Whidbey Island offer beautiful views.
